    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at MRL 2. Validation comparisons demonstrate NIH prediction agreement within 15% against available benchmark data. Relative hemolysis index RH < 1 at all five CPB operating points satisfies the acceptance criterion. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model provides sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
